title: HPE’s revenue up 14% to $9.7bn in Q4 2025
description: The company's networking revenue rose to $2.8bn, marking a 150% increase, with an operating profit margin of 23%, down from 24.4% previously.
content: Hewlett Packard Enterprise (HPE) has reported revenue of $9.7bn for the fourth quarter ended 31 October 2025 (Q4 2025), representing a 14% increase compared to $8.4bn during the same period last year… [+2778 chars]
